Waking Life;;87;;81;;R;;Transcending the boundaries of technology and imagination, "Waking Life" is a revolutionary breakthrough in film animation. In "Waking Life," Wiley Wiggins ("Dazed and Confused") travels through a series of encounters and observations in a world that may or may not be reality. It is this surreal existence, flourishing with endless ideas and possibilities, that ultimately leads to the question -- Are we sleep-walking through our waking state or wake-walking through our dreams?;;Drama,Animation;;Richard Linklater;;2001;;Wiley Wiggins,Trevor Jack Brooks,Lorelei Linklater,Glover Gill,Lara Hicks,Ames Asbell,Leigh Mahoney,Sara Nelson,Jeanine Attaway,Bill Wise,Robert Solomon,Kim Krizan,Eamonn Healy,Ethan Hawke,Julie Delpy,Charles Gunning,David Sosa,Alex Jones,Aklilu Gebrewald,Carol Dawson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/waking_life